---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About ideaoverflow.dev"
	description="Learn more about this blog and its purpose"
	pubDate={new Date('August 02 2025')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Welcome to ideaoverflow.dev - my personal corner of the internet where ideas come to life 
		and interesting discoveries find their home.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog serves as my digital repository for thoughts, fascinating articles I stumble upon, 
		and concepts that deserve deeper exploration. In our information-rich world, I believe in 
		curating and sharing the gems that make us think, learn, and grow.
	</p>

	<p>
		You'll find a mix of content here: technical insights, philosophical musings, book recommendations, 
		thought-provoking articles from around the web, and personal reflections on topics that capture 
		my curiosity. Each post is something I genuinely found valuable enough to share with the world.
	</p>

	<p>
		Thank you for stopping by, and I hope you find something here that sparks your own curiosity 
		or adds value to your day.
	</p>
</Layout>
